Package klingon.webserver.Beans

Class WeatherData

java.lang.Object
klingon.webserver.Beans.WeatherData
@Entity public class WeatherData extends Object
The WeatherData class is essentially a Java Bean class, which is used to encapsulate a number of objects into a single one. Hence this class encapsulates multiple WeatherData objects into a single one, namely this class (the bean).
